      "Text": "Security update for cockpit",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for cockpit fixes the following issues\n\n- CVE-2026-4802: remote command execution via unsanitized user-controlled parameters within crafted links in system logs\n  UI (bsc#1265040).\n- CVE-2026-25547: brace-expansion: unbounded brace range expansion can lead to excessive CPU and memory consumption and\n  may crash a Node.js process (bsc#1257836).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
